# Verible Lint Rules
# Documentation: https://chipsalliance.github.io/verible/lint.html

# Available rules can be listed with: verible-verilog-lint --help_rules

# Example rules:
+line-length=length:100
+no-trailing-spaces
+indentation=spaces:3
+no-tabs
+package-filename
+module-filename
+module-begin-block
+module-parameter-continuous-assign
+parameter-name-style=localparam_style:CAPITALIZED
+explicit-parameter-storage-type

# Disable specific rules by prefixing with -
